<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Chicken Note</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="edn187">  187  There is a slight sex-reversal at this point. Issy is &lsquo;la pau&rsquo; Leonie&rsquo; and the boys &lsquo;Josephinus&rsquo; and &lsquo;Mario-Louis.&rsquo; Note that in her single, stable form Issy is fond of Glugg and wants him to catch her, but in her diffuse form, as the rainbow girls, she simply despises his weaknesses. No doubt all of the dancing and the romancing in this episode, alongside the multiple personalities, would have put Joyce in mind of his own daughter Lucia.  </div>
